**Types of Powers**
the power-ups are shown in a row, Mario 3 style and player can use the next one in the queue by pressing space
  -Slow lasers (slows laser speed by 50%)
  -super speed (increase super speed by )
  -upgrade branches (all branches in the level are upgraded to gold level)

**Extra Lives**
every 10000 points, player gains an extra life

**Level Variations**
33% of the time get a random power up
15% of levels lasers should move left to right

**Difficulty Curve**
every five levels a different "theme"/different world
after reaching level 25, game should become an endless theme, that gets gradually harder
  -should have credits after level 25 -- "end of story"